# SHACL spec §2.1.3.5 — sh:targetObjectsOf data graph.
# Source: https://www.w3.org/TR/shacl/#targetObjectsOf
# Targets objects of ex:knows. The shape requires sh:nodeKind sh:IRI.
# ex:Bob ex:knows ex:Alice — ex:Alice is an IRI → conforms.
# ex:Alice ex:knows "Bob" — literal object → 1 violation.
PREFIX ex: <http://example.com/ns#>

ex:Bob ex:knows ex:Alice .
ex:Alice ex:knows "Bob" .
